{"tid":1627805,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"[勇武戰術post] 如何在陣地戰中有效打擊狗隻主力","createTime":"2019-10-05T18:01:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-06T11:48:41.000Z","uid":211761,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"a18fb18a9216c6cc93c28842cf55900ea5a2037d","tid":1627805,"uid":211761,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T18:01:02.000Z","msg":"最近幾個星期小妹開始由以前中後排人鏈 走上前線做前線<br />\n發現大家每次打陣地戰都有一個問題就係<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">無一個有效進攻的方法去殺傷狗隻</span></span></strong><br />\n但其實答案唔難 就係<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">錘砧戰術</span></span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n錘砧戰術 簡括而言 係用前線盾/傘陣吸引敵人注意/火力 再依靠機動部隊側翼包抄夾擊 <br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>所以係 盾/傘陣守 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 魔法師/打波既人攻 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></strong></span> <br />\n<br />\n咁現實例子係點呢? 套用10月1號黃大仙做例子<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UMGHc1J.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUMGHc1J.png&h=e29dfbf1&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n上面就係當日對峙情況, 3-4排傘陣+火魔法師在傘陣後搵機會<br />\n結果大家都知 -&gt; 防暴先掃射tg 速龍埋位沖過黎 傘陣頂唔住向後退 然後防線就崩潰 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n咁如果用左錘砧戰術會點?<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">首先傘陣維持同一陣地 但將進攻的人員防在兩翼 即是左邊的小巴站和右邊的正德街巴士總站</span></strong><br />\n <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cgVAx28.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcgVAx28.png&h=dcee9601&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n當防暴+速龍的陣線向前推 傘陣仍然會抵擋不住和後退 但兩翼的望攻人員就可以把握機會向前進攻 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CYcrEJx.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCYcrEJx.png&h=2efcc9e7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n就咁聽落去 好似好理想 而現實中錘砧戰術成功實行需要以下條件<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">1. 熟悉當區地理</span></strong><br />\n相當簡單 要識路先可以短時間內去到兩翼埋位進攻 同時亦都要知道點走佬 當對方察覺我們的意圖<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">2. 需要豐富經驗把握進攻時機</span></strong><br />\n由於對方都唔係企係度俾你打 當兩翼有威脅時 佢地都唔會推進<br />\n所以進攻人員需要先隱藏等待 再到適當時機 果斷進攻<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">3. 地理環境</span></strong><br />\n如果你係沙燕橋 就用唔到呢招 因為需要花費太多時間去對方兩翼<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">4. 對方陣型</span></strong><br />\n對方如果兩翼有重兵防守 我們的進攻人員反而會陷入險境<br />\n係這個我們無利的情況下 大家應該要決定係咪撤退去其他地點<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">5. 各方配合</span></strong><br />\n傘陣需要學識兩翼進攻時都要配合反進攻<br />\n哨兵需要提供資訊俾我們的進攻人員判斷進攻時機<br />\n<br />\n當呢個戰術實行到時 可以解決到<br />\n1. 火魔法只用黎燒路障/地下 <br />\n2. 陣地戰只會輸/退 對對方零傷害<br />\n3. 減少陣地戰被捕 (對方推進時 兩翼進攻人員可以打狗/救人)<br />\n<br />\n以下開放討論<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d0fc960db9c7279de24598bae4cac9e420618a7c","tid":1627805,"uid":211761,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T18:04:40.000Z","msg":"自推 1/10"},{"pid":"d44193cc9dcdb479318343c29d74d9f8c85dcfaa","tid":1627805,"uid":211761,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T18:04:50.000Z","msg":"自推 2/10"},{"pid":"a717ed5e2c0b2d97754e80395135d9c7c45fa767","tid":1627805,"uid":211761,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T18:05:04.000Z","msg":"自推 3/10"},{"pid":"1269a6d1d23b1d9dfd6a6381250ab66f33b6a2a2","tid":1627805,"uid":211761,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T18:05:19.000Z","msg":"自推 4/10"},{"pid":"87bcda47f52c473b2237798c2d23748595c871b1","tid":1627805,"uid":211761,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T18:05:29.000Z","msg":"自推 5/10"},{"pid":"cf2601090fe7ec1050d68ff7b89555f744b6a44a","tid":1627805,"uid":211761